{
  "frontCover": "Front cover of a birthday greeting card in a clean, minimalist, flat 2D illustration style. The background is a soft, creamy off-white. A simple line drawing of a rocket is depicted in the upper right quadrant, angled upwards and to the left. The rocket has a pointed nose cone, a circular window, and two swept-back fins. Trailing from the rocket is a thin, curved line representing exhaust, dotted with small, scattered shapes in coral orange and teal blue. Below the rocket's trajectory, in the lower center of the card, are the words \"happy birthday\" in a bold, sans-serif, black font. The text is centered horizontally and positioned to avoid the top and bottom 10% bleed area. The overall mood is playful and celebratory, with a touch of whimsy.",
  "backCover": "Back cover of a birthday greeting card, maintaining the clean, minimalist, flat 2D illustration style. The background is the same soft, creamy off-white as the front cover. A single, small, scattered dot in coral orange is positioned in the lower right corner, serving as a subtle, subtle continuation of the confetti motif from the front. No text or other elements are present, providing a peaceful and uncluttered conclusion to the card's visual narrative.",
  "leftInterior": "Left interior spread of a birthday greeting card in a clean, minimalist, flat 2D illustration style. The background is the same soft, creamy off-white. The composition features a stylized, abstract representation of a celestial pathway. A thin, wavy line, starting from the bottom left and arcing upwards towards the center, is rendered in black. Along this line are scattered, irregular dots and small dashes in coral orange and teal blue, mimicking the trail of the rocket from the front cover, but more spread out and delicate. This creates a sense of gentle movement and continuation of the journey theme, without featuring any characters or explicit imagery. The overall mood is serene and slightly whimsical, harmonizing with the front cover's playful tone.",
  "rightInterior": "Right interior spread of a birthday greeting card, continuing the clean, minimalist, flat 2D illustration style. The background is the same soft, creamy off-white. The central focus is the message text, carefully integrated into a decorative composition. The text reads: \"Jordan,\n\nHappy birthday! I was going to make a joke about you getting old, but then I remembered my own age and decided not to go there. Hope you have a fantastic day!\n\n- Craig\" This text is presented in a clear, black, sans-serif font, with \"Happy birthday\" slightly larger and bolder than the rest. The text block is positioned in the center, respecting the safe printing margins. To the upper right and lower left of the text block, subtle decorative elements mirroring the rocket's trail are present: thin, curved lines with scattered dots and dashes in coral orange and teal blue, suggesting a gentle burst of celebration. These elements are less dense than on the front, providing a soft framing for the message. The overall mood is warm, humorous, and personal, perfectly complementing the written sentiment."
}
